For the latest version and information about installing, go to http://www.astro.rug.nl/rfi-software/ .

You can compile the software by executing from the LOFAR directory:
mkdir build/gnu_opt
cmake ../.. -DCASACORE_ROOT_DIR=/home/anoko/projects/detectrfi-ext/install -DLOG4CPLUS_LIBRARY=/home/anoko/projects/detectrfi-ext/install/lib/liblog4cplus.a -DLOG4CPLUS_INCLUDE_DIR=/home/anoko/projects/detectrfi-ext/install/include/
